# Routing (Canonical)

## Sync policy

- **This file** is the source of truth for the route map.
- Implementations: `@src/client/AppRouter.tsx` (frontend), `@src/server.ts` (API).
- `docs/ROUTES.md` is a GitHub-friendly stub; do not edit it instead of this file.

## When changing routes

- Update tables below (path, method/access, description).
- Update navigation flow if user journey changed.
- Change code in the same PR: client + server + this rule.
- Remove stale rows when endpoints are deleted.

## Verification

- New route exists in code and in this file with identical path.
- Renames updated in client, server, and this file.

## Frontend Routes (Client)

Defined in [src/client/AppRouter.tsx](src/client/AppRouter.tsx).

| Path | Access | Component | Description |
|------|--------|-----------|-------------|
| `/` | guest+ | CatalogPage (HomePage) | Main catalog, tabs: All / My works |
| `/catalog` | guest+ | CatalogPage | Same as `/`. Query: `filter=mine`, `author`, `translator`, `tag` (entity IDs for filtering) |
| `/about` | guest+ | AboutPage | About Arcane |
| `/contact` | guest+ | ContactPage | Contact info |
| `/privacy` | guest+ | PrivacyPage | Privacy policy |
| `/terms` | guest+ | TermsPage | Terms of service |
| `/profile` | user+ | ProfilePage | Profile: reading history, settings, avatar |
| `/projects` | author+ | ProjectsPage | Projects grid (AuthorGate) |
| `/admin/entities` | admin+ | AdminEntitiesPage | Admin panel for global entities (AdminGate) |
| `/projects/:projectId` | author+ | ProjectPage | Project overview (AuthorGate) |
| `/projects/:projectId/chapters/:chapterId` | author+ | ChapterPage | Chapter editing (AuthorGate). Query: `search` - pre-fill and auto-open find-in-chapter (e.g. from ReportsModal) |
| `/projects/:projectId/chapters/:chapterId/reading` | author+ | ReadingModePage | Reading mode (AuthorGate) |
| `/projects/:projectId/reading` | author+ | ReadingModePage | Reading mode, first chapter (AuthorGate) |
| `/p/:publicationId` | guest+ | PublicationPage | Public publication page |
| `/p/:publicationId/chapters/:chapterId/reading` | guest+ | PublicationReadingPage | Reading mode for public publication |

### Access Levels

- **guest+** - anyone (including unauthenticated)
- **user+** - requires `role: user` or higher (guest redirects to `/?login=required`)
- **author+** - requires `role: author` or higher (user sees UpgradeScreen)
- **admin+** - requires `role: admin` (non-admin users see access denied)

### Protected routes

When guest visits `/profile`, `/projects`, `/projects/*`, `/admin/entities`, or `/admin/*`, redirect to `/?login=required` and open AuthModal.

