## API Routes (Server)

Defined in [src/server.ts](src/server.ts).

### Validation (Zod)

Most API endpoints validate request body and query parameters using Zod schemas from [src/api/schemas/](src/api/schemas/). On validation failure, the API returns `400` with:

```json
{
  "error": "Validation failed",
  "details": { "fieldName": ["error message"] }
}
```

