## Token Usage

Token usage indicator is shown only on paths where it's relevant. See [src/client/utils/tokenUsagePaths.ts](src/client/utils/tokenUsagePaths.ts):

- `/projects` - projects grid
- `/projects/:id` - project page (except `/reading`)

